<h1>Directory of Hazards and Extremes Resources</h1>

    <p>
        <a href="/">Home</a> >
            <a href="/News">News</a>  >             <a href="/News/Weather">Weather</a>  >             <a href="/News/Weather/Hazards_and_Extremes">Hazards and Extremes</a>         </p>

<p><p>Forecasts and warnings for various severe weather conditions, information on preparing for disasters, and news coverage of major weather events.</p></p>

