<h2>Resources in This Category</h2>
<ul>

    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.mherrera.org/temp.htm" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Extreme Temperatures</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.mherrera.org/temp.htm</strong></font> <br /> Recorded from hundreds of localities around the world.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.hail.org/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Hail.org</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.hail.org/</strong></font> <br /> Provides forecasts for some parts of the US. Supplies maps and pictures.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://forecast.weather.gov/product_types.php?site=NWS?thumbs=on" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>National Weather Service: Active Warnings</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://forecast.weather.gov/product_types.php?site=NWS?thumbs=on</strong></font> <br /> Current weather warnings and special weather advisories from the National Weather Service.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.cpc.noaa.gov/products/predictions/threats/threats.php" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>National Weather Service: Climate Prediction Center</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.cpc.noaa.gov/products/predictions/threats/threats.php</strong></font> <br /> Long-range assessment of weather threats, including drought, heavy rain, tropical systems and El Nino/La Nina events.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.spc.noaa.gov/products/wwa/index.html" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>National Weather Service: Storm Prediction Center</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.spc.noaa.gov/products/wwa/index.html</strong></font> <br /> Provides updated severe weather information.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="https://alerts.weather.gov/cap/us.php?x=1" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>National Weather Service: Warnings Area</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>https://alerts.weather.gov/cap/us.php?x=1</strong></font> <br /> Immediate access to all available warnings for the United States, including tornado, hurricane, and winter weather warnings.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.spc.noaa.gov/products/spcmdrss.xml" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Storm Prediction Center Mesoscale Discussions</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.spc.noaa.gov/products/spcmdrss.xml</strong></font> <br /> Feed provides US NOAA mesoscale discussions of weather systems with the potential to generate tornadoes or severe thunderstorms.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.spc.noaa.gov/products/spcwwrss.xml" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Storm Prediction Center Tornado/Severe Thunderstorm Watches</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.spc.noaa.gov/products/spcwwrss.xml</strong></font> <br /> Feed provides notices of US NOAA severe storm watches.</p>
    </li>	
</ul>

